                <p class="hca-typography--body-1">Default to using a flat button until there is a need for a more important action to highlight. This card-based interface can have many buttons come into view all with separate contexts for their actions. It would be hard to call out any one button for the primary action in this scenario.</p>
              </figcaption>
            </figure>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <figure class="hca-visual-example hca-visual-example--mobile">
              <img src="{{page.base_url}}images/components/buttons/button-choice-raised-example.png" class="img-responsive hca-visual-example__comp" alt="If/when you have multiple actions available, you can use a raised button to highlight the most important action." />
