    <article id="section-button-placement" class="app-section">
      <h2 class="app-article-headline hca-typography--headline">Button Placement</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-5">
          <div class="hca-layout__container--body-content">
            <p class="hca-typography--body-1">If you have multiple actions presented to a user, where one action is affirmative and one action is dismissive, always place the affirmative action to the right of the dismissive action.</p>
            <p class="hca-typography--body-1">This pattern will appear often in <a href="{{page.base_url}}components/dialogs" target="_blank">dialogs</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-7 text-center">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
